snippet.title: Speaking Simulator [Switch/PC] Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Speaking Simulator is an awkwardly hilarious physics game where an android struggles to appear human by flopping its lips and tongue around.


Speaking Simulator aims to dominate the human race through inane social interactions on Nintendo Switch starting January 30, 2020, launching simultaneously alongside the previously announced PC/Mac versions coming to Steam.
